{"tid":2283733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國最高法院多數法官似乎準備維持《奧巴馬醫保》","createTime":"2020-11-12T20:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T02:11:14.000Z","uid":295230,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ba6fd38ca5c2b3c5200943ce42599e9111ba22","tid":2283733,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:26:07.000Z","msg":"美國最高法院的多數大法官星期二(11月10日)示意，最高法院有可能駁回共和黨人試圖廢除美國《平價醫療法》的訴求。這部法律為千百萬美國人提供醫療保險。九名大法官在華盛頓舉行了一次聽證。兩名保守派大法官---首席大法官約翰&middot;羅伯茨和大法官布雷特&middot;卡瓦諾都示意，他們傾向於加入法庭的三位自由派大法官，繼續維持這部法律。<br />\n<br />\n《平價醫療法》俗稱《奧巴馬醫保》，由前總統奧巴馬（Barack Obama）於2010年 3月 23日簽署成為法律，是自1965年通過聯邦醫療保險和聯邦醫療補助之後，最重要的監管改革，還有擴大的覆蓋範圍，但從成為法律開始就遭共和黨人強烈反對。"},{"pid":"d004fd474f4023e57c55f9ca6b9b01c8edb4af1a","tid":2283733,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:27:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/supreme-court-obamacare/5656590.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fsupreme-court-obamacare%2F5656590.html&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=da38a3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/supreme-court-obamacare/5656590.html</a>"},{"pid":"4b0128efdd55b25bfbf2458899f727c22470798e","tid":2283733,"uid":261913,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:27:35.000Z","msg":"咁判對牙祖不利喎<br />\n判完呢單有利dem 下一戰就係侵侵選舉戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc4939c55b40b951829a4b1dd5133b1ba91794d","tid":2283733,"uid":226955,"like":56,"dislike":4,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:28:13.000Z","msg":"呢啲內政事務我唔理，最緊要萬眾一心同我打柒聖經嗰隻大紅龍就可以啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f25d6964456d6faf19f95e8fbc663e2221b94c7","tid":2283733,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T20:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s